# Runtime state lives under .pi/orchestrator/.
#
# `.sages/` is kept gitignored as a working area for in-flight design
# work (e.g. `pi/.sages/designs/<date>-<topic>.md` brainstorming
# drafts, `pi/.sages/workspace/execution.yaml` legacy qiaochui
# decomposition output, `.sages/snapshots/<id>.bak` from the planned
# AFT migration's `aft/safety.ts` T7 task). The active 4-tool
# orchestrator writes ONLY to `.pi/orchestrator/` — see
# `pi/src/tools/orchestrator/types.ts:198` for `ORCHESTRATOR_DIR`.
.sages/

# Plan files (generated)
.plan/

